&lt;a class="linkcard-a" href="https://www.nqou.net/2026/01/26/002040/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" title="https://www.nqou.net/2026/01/26/002040/" aria-label="https://www.nqou.net/2026/01/26/002040/"&gt;
